\c 14
\s Ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* mayelana lembalela
\p
\v 1 Ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* elafika kuJeremiya mayelana lendaba zembalela.
\v 2 UJuda uyalila, lamasango akhe adangele; amnyama kuze kube semhlabathini, lokukhala kweJerusalema kwenyukile.
\v 3 Njalo izikhulu zakhe zithuma abancinyane bazo emanzini; bafika emithonjeni, bangatholi manzi; babuyele inkonxa zabo zingelalutho, belenhloni, beyangekile, bembomboze ikhanda labo.
\v 4 Ngoba umhlabathi udabukile, ngoba kungekho izulu elizweni, abalimi balenhloni, bambomboza ikhanda labo.
\v 5 Yebo impala layo iyazala egangeni, i\add ku\add*tshiye, ngoba kungelatshani.
\v 6 Labobabhemi beganga bayema emadundulwini, baphembele umoya\x + 2.24.\x* njengemigobho;\x + Hlab. 44.19; 74.13.\x* amehlo abo ayaphela, ngoba kungelatshani.
\p
\v 7 Lanxa izono zethu zifakaza zimelana lathi, N\nd kosi\nd*, yenza ngenxa yebizo lakho\x + 14.21; Hlab. 25.11.\x*; ngoba ukuhlehlela nyovane kwethu kunengi\x + 2.19.\x*, sonile kuwe\x + 14.20.\x*.
\v 8 Wena themba likaIsrayeli, uMsindisi wakhe ngesikhathi sembandezelo, kungani uzakuba njengowezizweni elizweni\x + 17.13; Hlab. 71.5; Jer. 50.7.\x*, lanjengesihambi \add e\add*siphambukela eceleni ukulala ubusuku\x + 9.2.\x*?
\v 9 Kungani uzakuba njengomuntu odidekileyo, njengeqhawe \add e\add*lingelakusindisa\x + Isa. 59.1.\x*. Kanti wena uphakathi kwethu, N\nd kosi\nd*, lebizo lakho libizwe phezu kwethu\x + Eks. 29.45.\x*; ungasitshiyi\x + Hlab. 119.121.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* ngalababantu: Ngokunjalo bathanda ukuzula, kabazinqandanga inyawo zabo; ngakho iN\nd kosi\nd* kayithokozi ngabo\x + Hos. 8.13.\x*, khathesi izakhumbula ububi babo, izihambele izono zabo\x + Hos. 8.13.\x*.
\p
\v 11 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kimi: Ungakhulekeli lababantu\x + 7.16.\x* kube kuhle\x + 21.10; 24.5,6; 39.16; 44.27; 15.11; Hlab. 86.17.\x*.
\v 12 Lapho bezila ukudla, kangiyikuzwa ukukhala kwabo\x + Zaga 1.28; Isa. 58.3.\x*; lalapho benikela umnikelo wokutshiswa lomnikelo wokudla, kangiyikuthokoza ngabo; kodwa ngizabaqeda\x + 16.4; 44.27; Jer. 14.15; 9.16.\x* ngenkemba\x + 24.10; 27.8,13; 32.24,36; 34.17; Hez. 14.21; 15.2.\x* langendlala langomatshayabhuqe wesifo\x + 24.10; 27.8,13; 32.24,36; 34.17; Hez. 14.21; Jer. 15.2.\x*.
\v 13 Ngasengisithi: Hawu, Nkosi Jehova! Khangela, abaprofethi bathi kubo: Kaliyikubona inkemba, kaliyikuba lendlala\x + 4.10.\x*, kodwa ngizalinika ukuthula okuqinisekileyo kulindawo\x + 6.14.\x*.
\v 14 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kimi: Abaprofethi baprofetha amanga ngebizo lami\x + 20.6; 23.25; 27.10; Jer. 5.31.\x*. Kangibathumanga, njalo kangibalayanga, njalo kangikhulumanga kibo; baprofetha kini umbono wamanga\x + 14.15; 23.21; 27.15; 29.9; Hez. 13.6; Dute. 18.20; Mat. 7.15.\x*, lokuhlahlula, lokuyize\x + 27.9; 29.8; Dute. 18.10.\x*, lenkohliso yenhliziyo yabo\x + 23.26.\x*.
\v 15 Ngakho itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* mayelana labaprofethi abaprofetha ebizweni lami, ngoba mina ngingabathumanga\x + 14.15; 23.21; 27.15; 29.9; Hez. 13.6; Dute. 18.20; Mat. 7.15.\x*, kanti bathi\x + 5.12.\x*: Inkemba lendlala kakuyikuba khona kulelilizwe: Ngenkemba langendlala labobaprofethi bazaqedwa\x + 44.12; 23.30; Jer. 14.12.\x*.
\v 16 Labantu, abaprofetha kibo, bazakuba ngabaphoselwa ezitaladeni zeJerusalema ngenxa yendlala lenkemba; njalo kungekho obangcwabayo\x + Hlab. 79.3.\x*, bona, omkabo, lamadodana abo, lamadodakazi abo; ngoba ngizathululela ububi babo phezu kwabo.
\p
\v 17 Ngakho uzakutsho lelilizwi kibo \add elokuthi\add*: Amehlo ami kawehlise inyembezi ebusuku lemini\x + 9.18; 9.1; Lilo 2.18.\x*, zingakhawuli\x + Lilo 3.49.\x*, ngoba intombi emsulwa yabantu bami yephukile \add ngo\add*kwephuka okukhulu\x + 8.21.\x*, ukutshaywa okubuhlungu kakhulu\x + Hez. 7.15.\x*.
\v 18 Uba ngiphumela emaphandleni, khangela-ke, ababulewe ngenkemba\x + Hez. 7.15.\x*. Njalo uba ngingena emzini, khangela-ke, abagulayo ngendlala\x + Hez. 7.15.\x*. Yebo, bobabili umprofethi lompristi\x + 5.31; 6.13.\x* babhodabhoda\x + Gen. 34.10,21; 42.34.\x* elizweni kodwa bengazi\x + 15.14.\x*.
\p
\v 19 Usumalile isibili uJuda yini? Umphefumulo wakho unengwa yiZiyoni yini\x + Lilo 5.22.\x*? Usitshayeleni njalo singabi lokwelatshwa\x + 15.18.\x*? \add Sa\add*lindela ukuthula, kodwa kakubanga lokuhle\x + 8.15.\x*; lesikhathi sokwelatshwa, kodwa khangela, uvalo\x + 8.15.\x*.
\v 20 Siyazi, N\nd kosi\nd*, ukukhohlakala kwethu \add lo\add*bubi babobaba, ngoba sonile kuwe\x + 8.15.\x*.
\v 21 Unga\add si\add*deleli, ngenxa yebizo lakho\x + 14.7.\x*, ungayangisi isihlalo sobukhosi sodumo lwakho; khumbula, ungasephuli isivumelwano sakho lathi\x + Hlab. 106.45; Levi 26.42.\x*.
\v 22 Kukhona yini phakathi\x + Jobe 38.28; Zek. 10.1,2.\x* kokuyize kwabezizwe okunganisa izulu\x + Dute. 32.21; Jer.2.5.\x*? Kumbe amazulu anganika izihlambo yini\x + 3.3.\x*? Akusuwe yini, N\nd kosi\nd*, Nkulunkulu wethu? Ngakho sizalindela kuwe\x + Isa. 30.23; 10.13; Jobe 5.10; Jer. 5.24.\x*; ngoba nguwe owenze zonke lezizinto\x + Isa. 66.2; Jobe 12.9.\x*.